metadata.name: Gangstapes #1
metadata.description: GangstApes is a story and community-driven, hand-drawn NFT collection and Street brand that has been summoned on the Ethereum blockchain. We ARE A TEAM OF SKILLED AND INTERESTING PEOPLE THAT HAVE A LOT TO OFFER TO THE WEB3 WORLD. WE WILL NEVER AGREE TO GOVERNMENT RULES - BUT TRANSITIONING INTO WEB3 FROM TRADITIONAL SOFTWARE DEVELOPMENT, ART AND SOCIAL MEDIA IS CHALLENGING. WE INTEND TO USE THIS MINT AS A WAY TO EXPERIMENT AND GROW A COMMUNITY OF EXCLUSIVE OPEN MINDED GANGSTERS, TO STEWARD AND CREATE A COMMUNITY OF ART FANS WHO WANT TO SEE A SMALL TEAM LEARN THE ROPES OF WEB3 AND BRING COOL IDEAS TO LIFE WITH THE FEEDBACK OF OUR BELOVED GANGSTAPES.
